 Our Areas of Expertise 











Institutional
As a core part of our business, we work with more than 100 major pension funds, endowments and foundations across Canada to invest for long-term performance excellence.








Private Client
We are dedicated to helping our high net worth clients meet and exceed their investment goals within a value-based portfolio framework.








Sub-Advisory
We create partnerships with investment firms who want their individual clients to have access to our institutional money management expertise.





 













