Company Overview of Foyston, Gordon & Payne Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Foyston, Gordon & Payne Inc. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm provides advisory services to individuals, typically high net worth individuals. It also manages accounts for pension and profit sharing plans, foundations, endowments, pooled investment vehicles, charitable organizations, corporations, and state or municipal government entities. The firm launches and manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm conducts in-house research to make its investments. It was founded in 1980 and is based in Toronto, Canada with an additional office in Montreal, Canada. Foyston...
Foyston, Gordon & Payne Inc. is a privately owned investment manager. The firm provides advisory services to individuals, typically high net worth individuals. It also manages accounts for pension and profit sharing plans, foundations, endowments, pooled investment vehicles, charitable organizations, corporations, and state or municipal government entities. The firm launches and manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm conducts in-house research to make its investments. It was founded in 1980 and is based in Toronto, Canada with an additional office in Montreal, Canada. Foyston, Gordon & Payne operates as a subsidiary of AMG Canada Corp.
Detailed Description


