Foyston, Gordon & Payne Inc. Key Developments

Foyston, Gordon & Payne Inc. Appoints Stephen Mitchell as Senior Vice President and Portfolio Manager of Global Equities
Oct 6 16
Foyston, Gordon & Payne Inc. announced the appointment of Stephen Mitchell as Senior Vice President and Portfolio Manager. Stephen spent 23 years with Burgundy Asset Management Ltd., most recently as portfolio manager of global and U.S. large cap equity portfolios. He brings a proven track record and has built a reputation as a disciplined and thorough value-oriented investment analyst and portfolio manager. Stephen will manage FGP's global and international equity mandates.


